Class AttributeManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mosedb.tools.AttributeManager

  • public class AttributeManager
extends java.lang.Object
    AttributeManager is a class that handles all the attribute-setting, getting and removing from the session. The code is self-explanatory.
